{"tid":859422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jackson Wang 王嘉爾傳授學習韓語祕訣!!","createTime":"2018-10-12T13:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T14:30:51.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc04182332f6dfb3d7f506c789f999256d3947f","tid":859422,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images6.fanpop.com/image/photos/37200000/-Jackson-jackson-got7-37275188-1000-1500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages6.fanpop.com%2Fimage%2Fphotos%2F37200000%2F-Jackson-jackson-got7-37275188-1000-1500.jpg&h=fe2424ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGOT7成員Jackson於10日出演了《請給一頓飯》，在節目中被李敬揆問到：「來到韓國已經是第幾年了？」Jackson回答：「在韓國生活已經第七年了。」<br />\n<br />\n接著自爆：「只有第一年是用書學習韓語，在那之後是<span style=\"color: red;\">靠戀愛學習韓語的</span>！」<br />\nJackson表示：「觀眾們可能有所不知，但老實說這個方法真的是最快的！」<br />\nJackson接著補充：「要學習某一種語言的話，除了語言本身，也要去理解那個國家的文化才行！」<br />\n除此之外，還必須兼具幽默感及掌握談話中的笑點，如果是這樣的話，除了戀愛之外，並沒有其他方法可以學到阿~<br />\nJackson還說：「難道這些秘訣會在書裡出現嗎？！」因此最適合外國人使用的《訓民正音》就是「戀愛」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/landscape/public/images/methode/2018/06/04/7a42d092-625c-11e8-82ea-2acc56ad2bf7_1280x720_162313.JPG?itok=L8ICdt24\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.i-scmp.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flandscape%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F7a42d092-625c-11e8-82ea-2acc56ad2bf7_1280x720_162313.JPG%3Fitok%3DL8ICdt24&h=33843c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n接著李敬揆又問Jackson：「談了幾年的戀愛？」<span style=\"color: red;\">Jackson回答自己當時談了兩年半至三年的戀愛，在那之後韓語實力立刻暴風成長</span><br />\n<br />\nJackson接著又說：「如果問我在談戀愛時因為什麼事情才讓韓語能力大為進步的話，答案就是吵架！」<br />\n想要表達自己內心的想法，卻因為語言的限制處於劣勢，在煩躁大爆發的情況下，燃起了學習韓語的強烈意志！<br />\n結果當被問到：「之前都是因為什麼事情才吵架？」時，Jackson表示：「因為以前年紀小，所以幾乎都是為了一些很不像話的事情爭吵。」舉例來說：「傳訊息的時候沒有傳表情符號...」<br />\n<br />\n這麼誠實的Jackson真的是太好笑啦XD 一起來看看影片吧~"},{"pid":"65e615b249d2b53085243c810fb6179049b39544","tid":859422,"uid":173631,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T13:26:37.000Z","msg":"e條柒頭點解咁撚紅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c6d3b52fb7c828e31b465e74fc31472d381867","tid":859422,"uid":190258,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"65e615b249d2b53085243c810fb6179049b39544","tid":859422,"uid":173631,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T13:26:37.000Z","msg":"e條柒頭點解咁撚紅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T13:32:47.000Z","msg":"夠假<br />\n支那人最鐘意"},{"pid":"6856f4f1975c9c537187cadd1d48950f469f54b5","tid":859422,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"嘉爾bb好skr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0898983ff5a4d5d22b79cffaa529af0544f9af","tid":859422,"uid":63057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"外國人練習生拍拖9成9都係揾返同公司練習生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7794a2f2ad2c7805d5bccacae21027838314e3c","tid":859422,"uid":63057,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"65e615b249d2b53085243c810fb6179049b39544","tid":859422,"uid":173631,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T13:26:37.000Z","msg":"e條柒頭點解咁撚紅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"認真答<br />\nKpop出身<br />\n靚仔又大隻<br />\n有才華，唱歌跳舞都有實力<br />\n風趣搞笑<br />\n人品好"},{"pid":"f084d67e02e8af33d4937b38696d6e3dd860ee9e","tid":859422,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e0898983ff5a4d5d22b79cffaa529a